full_text:
A BLUEPRINT FOR SUCCESS
It hàs been said, that if the whole race would at an agreed moment,
scuff their feet, the planet would actually slow down. Ah, yes,
causing a change in the moon, the tides and many earthly dynamics.
Of course, my real topic is not physics...but it is about what can
happen when -
-- ambitious ideas are conceived
when, -- plans are meticiously and well laid
and what, -- unity and hardwork can achieve.
We all know the achievements of the past 20 months or so were no
accident. We were not touched by a wave of a wand. No witchcraft was
left to chance. And no one scuffed the wrong way.
00138494
We had a plan.
We had a set of goals.
